?? Defining the hadamrd minus (|->) quantum state
<?
    The Q Assembly type system automatically understands 
    that this is not a quantum gate 
    but a quantum state.
?>
minus (
    (H)*|0>
)

{
    {(minus)}
    {(H)*(minus)}
}
    -> <

